OL,3,CFirst the pints, now the pain: Can
OL,4,CWolves end their season's woes?
OL,6,FFor a brief moment Vitor Pereira
OL,7,Funited a fanbase. Out drinking with
OL,8,Fsupporters after wins, he was the down-
OL,9,Fto-earth boss who made Wolves tick.
OL,11,FThat's why it is so sad to see the
OL,12,Fbreakdown in his relationship with the
OL,13,Fclub's fans in just six months.
OL,15,FThe nadir was reached on Sunday as he
OL,16,Fwas dragged away from the South Bank
OL,17,Fwith fans chanting "You're getting
OL,18,Fsacked in the morning".
