OL,3,CFirst the pints, now the pain: Can
OL,4,CWolves end their season's woes?
OL,6,FDid that really happen ? It's not on
OL,7,Fvideo is it ? The questions that so
OL,8,Foften follow a heavy night. Added to
OL,9,Fthe hanxiety is the very real threat
OL,10,Fthat Wolves are going to be relegated.
OL,12,FWith just two points from nine games,
OL,13,Fthis is even worse than Gary O'Neil's
OL,14,Fstart to last season.
OL,16,FO'Neil had terrible fixtures that
OL,17,Fsucked the confidence from the squad
OL,18,Fbut Pereira's side have already lost
OL,19,Fagainst all three promoted clubs.
