OL,3,CFirst the pints, now the pain: Can
OL,4,CWolves end their season's woes?
OL,6,FYou couldn't say they're favourites
OL,7,Ffor a match now until December 3 when
OL,8,Fthey face fellow strugglers Nottingham
OL,9,FForest.
OL,11,FThe general ire of fans is first
OL,12,Ftowards the owners Fosun. They took
OL,13,FWolves to the heights of European
OL,14,Ffootball but have shown a lack of
OL,15,Fambition since.
OL,17,FThey are poor at showing and
OL,18,Farticulating that they care.
