OL,3,CFirst the pints, now the pain: Can
OL,4,CWolves end their season's woes?
OL,6,FWolves have sold their best players in
OL,7,Frecent years but they broke tradition
OL,8,Fto keep hold of Stand Larsen this
OL,9,Fsummer when Newcastle wanted him.
OL,11,FTaking the emotion out of it, the
OL,12,Fmodel of buying low to sell high has
OL,13,Fworked for Wolves, but it now shows
OL,14,Fsigns of breaking with disastrous
OL,15,Fconsequences.
OL,17,FLadislav Krejci is possibly the only
OL,18,Fsummer signing who anyone else in the
OL,19,FPremier League would take right now.
OL,20,FThat's not to say the others can't
OL,21,Fturn things round.
