OL,3,CFirst the pints, now the pain: Can
OL,4,CWolves end their season's woes?
OL,6,FTheir task is easier than Pereira's.
OL,7,FHe needs to get a result against
OL,8,FChelsea on Wednesday night in the only
OL,9,Fcompetition that's given them joy so
OL,10,Ffar this season.
OL,12,FWolves are the only Midlands team left
OL,13,Fin the Carabao Cup.
OL,15,FIf they're still in it after Chelsea
OL,16,Fcome to town then maybe, just maybe,
OL,17,FPereira won't have had his last night
OL,18,Fout in Wolverhampton.
